[normal] ‘parent’ of a growing cluster of schools, run by the associated G Trust
[normal];
[normal]H [bold]Primary, a large primary which has so far remained
[normal] with the local authority;
[normal]J [bold]Comprehensive, an ‘outstanding’ academy
[normal];
[normal]K[bold] School, less successful secondary school, being supported 
[normal]by J
[normal];
